cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.CL

The paper deals with point cloud processing using convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also proposes a new approach for designing neural networks, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The experiments conducted in the paper involve shape classification and segmentation, which are tasks related to graphics (cs.GR) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
